---
title: Golden Coconut Prawn Curry with Garlic Rice & Coriander
description: Embark on a culinary journey with our golden curry, a harmonious blend of tender prawns bathed in a rich coconutty sauce. With pops of carrot and green beans throughout, this exotic dish promises a perfect balance of freshness and creaminess.
